cs.LG, cs.CY, cs.CE, cs.HC, cs.DB 

This paper involves the development of machine learning models to predict the risk of uncontrolled hypertension using electronic health records data. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other likely categories include cs.CY (Computers and Society), cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science), cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction), and cs.DB (Databases).
